data.meta_site_name: Brian O'Brien Obituary | April 26, 2021 | Myrtle Beach, SC
data.text:
Brian Francis O'Brien, age 68 of Myrtle Beach passed away Monday, April 26, 2021 at Embrace Hospice House.

Born in Brooklyn, NY, he is the son of the late Raymond and Agnes O'Brien.

He is survived by his domestic partner, Edward Thomas Fisher.

No services are planned at this time.
